				<div class="c-content-tile__description">
					<p>Not only is Squalane good for your skin–it is actually naturally present in skin. Found plentifully in your skin’s sebum until your early 20s, Squalane begins to deplete with age which can leave skin prone to rough and dry areas. Using a facial cleanser with Squalane can help protect skin’s barrier and seal in moisture for softer, smoother skin.</p>
