						<div class="c-accordion__content-inner" itemscope="" itemprop="acceptedAnswer" itemtype="https://schema.org/Answer"> 

							<div itemprop="text">

								<!-- START ANSWER copy HTML markup-->
								<p>The Kiehl’s approach is recommending the appropriate ingredients and formulas to help each person’s skin achieve its optimal healthy balance. With that in mind, we formulate products at pH levels appropriate to stabilize our ingredients and formulas to maintain their quality, safety and efficacy for their entire shelf lives. While pH levels can vary by product, we always ensure that the total formulation, including pH, is appropriate for product efficacy, tolerability, and respect for skin barrier.</p>
								<!-- END ANSWER copy HTML markup-->

							</div>

						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
